headline: Jacobs Solutions’ Quarterly Earnings Preview: What You Need to Know
summary: Jacobs Solutions is set to release its fourth-quarter results next month, and analysts are expecting a double-digit increase in earnings, reflecting solid project momentum and continued operational strength.
